title: Vacation Spots
name: Vacation Spots
description:
A Map by Sofa89

Vacations over the last year.

properties.name: Atlanta
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I went to the Georgia Aquarium with some people. It\'s one of the largest aquariums. It\'s one of the only aquariums with beluga whales.

properties.name: Chattanooga
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I spent the day in Chattanooga just walking around and hanging out.

properties.name: De Soto
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89My boyfriends grandparents and relatives live in De Soto. We went up there to visit. We go on float trips where we just float down the river. So here\'s a picture of the group that went.

properties.name: Disney World
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I went to Disney World over the summer with my boyfriend and his family. We spent a week there and it was amazing!

properties.name: Gatlinburg
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I went to the Aquarium with my boyfriend and spent the day in Gatlinburg.

properties.name: Hilton Head Island
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I went on a mother-daughter beach trip to Hilton Head. We spent a week and it was a whole lot of fun.

properties.name: Johnson City
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I visited my best friend for her birthday. I go a couple times a year.

properties.name: New York, NY
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89My family and I went on an amazing trip to New York last May!! It was the first time my brother and I had been there and we loved it. This is a picture of my brother and I on Ellis Island with Manhattan in the background.

properties.name: Okaloosa Island
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89We went on a family vacation at Okaloosa Island. It\'s close to Destin.

properties.name: St. Louis
properties.description: Posted by Sofa89I went up to Missouri with my boyfriends family to visit their relatives. We went to St. Louis to go shopping.
